314 contain, transport or otherwise package raw, uncooked or butchered meat, poultry, fish,
325 seafood or eggs will instead be repealed July 1, 2027.
3 3. It provides that the provision of that law that is currently set to be repealed July 1,
4 2025 and provides an exemption from that law for a covered establishment to sell at retail
5 food or beverages in or on a polystyrene foam disposable food service container that the
6 covered establishment purchases prepackaged at wholesale will instead be repealed July 1,
7 2027.
